node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Steffan on September 03, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text:
'Your World - International another Photographic Competition on the Environment' 1991-1992 - "To coincide with the Earth Summits twentieth anniversary the United Nations Environment Programme 'UNEP' held a photography competition in partnership with Canon. Contestants were asked to express their visions of the world either in celebration or condemnation of its present condition. With 32,000 entries from 144 countries this book contains 214 of the outstanding images submitted.." via @another___kind 

#world #planet #pollution #climatechange #ozone #earth #planet #planetearth #design #photography #photographer #photo #designer #architecture #architect #setdesign #cars #babies #ice #weather #holiday
